75
00:07:29,157 --> 00:07:31,076
Larry, just look
at the photo here.

76
00:07:32,286 --> 00:07:34,454
- [stammers] I wanna go home.
- Okay, but is she...

77
00:07:35,414 --> 00:07:37,214
- I wanna go home.
- Okay, I'll take you home.

78
00:07:37,291 --> 00:07:38,434
- I'll take you home.
- [Larry] Okay.

79
00:07:38,458 --> 00:07:40,502
- [Chris] Larry, it's okay.
- It's okay.

80
00:07:41,128 --> 00:07:42,462
