and you respect ours.

96
00:08:55,369 --> 00:08:56,537
[indistinct chatter]

97
00:08:58,205 --> 00:08:59,831
Fuck your sandbox.

98
00:09:02,668 --> 00:09:03,794
I don't know.

99
00:09:03,877 --> 00:09:05,254
It was the way he said,

100
00:09:05,337 --> 00:09:08,090
