picked me for the job.

139
00:11:14,299 --> 00:11:15,300
Yeah?

140
00:11:15,384 --> 00:11:17,636
Yeah, I'm not sure there
ever was anybody else.

141
00:11:17,719 --> 00:11:20,806
I got black belts in
karate and tae kwon do,

142
00:11:20,889 --> 00:11:24,935
