handle himself.

151
00:12:01,597 --> 00:12:03,891
Personable,
non-threatening demeanor,

152
00:12:03,974 --> 00:12:06,018
and he doesn't have an
ego that announces itself

153
00:12:06,101 --> 00:12:08,145
