182
00:14:32,164 --> 00:14:33,790
Where are you with the file?

183
00:14:35,501 --> 00:14:36,502
I…

184
00:14:37,461 --> 00:14:40,047
Yeah, I've been looking at the
Jessica Roach killing again,

185
